                            </p>
                          <p>
                              <em>MOHOLY-NAGY / IN MOTION</em>, Museum of Modern Art, Hayama, Hayama, 04/16/2011 - 07/10/2011; The National Museum of Modern Art, Kyoto, 07/20/2011 - 09/04/2011; Kawamura Memorial Museum of Art, 09/17/2011 - 12/11/2011
                            </p>
                          <p>
                              <em>The Paintings of Moholy-Nagy: The Shape of Things to Come</em>, Santa Barbara Museum of Art, Santa Barbara, 07/05/2015 - 09/27/2015
                            </p>
